name: Blockade
overview: -Original Story: 10 players challenged you to prove their skills. Show them You're better! This is a small game, made in 2 days. -Controls on original machine: Start the game: Start Move: Cursor Keys (Left - Right) Fire: A This is a homebrought game, run on Gameboy Pocket. A game by: László Rajcsányi - Wilds, 2021. Created with GB-Studio 2.0.0-beta5 by Chris Maltby! This game is an entry for the Gameboy Competition 2021. (https://itch.io/jam/gbcompo21)
